reviewText: A total flop in every way.  Hang your head in shame!  Change your names!  Be ashamed...be very ashamed for anyone to know you were 'ass'ociated with this rank giant stinker!  Once again they tricked us into paying for a flop without a trailer, shame on them too!
Love a good b-movie sc-fi and this is just great. So innocent and raw.
One of those b-movies that you'll love for it's honesty. Great stuff!
This was made in the desperate hope to piggy back on the star wars success but instead it was made on a credit card budget by ametures.  Almost as good as watching a blind T-Rex wrap Christmas gifts.
